videos.description: Morgan William finds Dominique Dillingham for the 3-pointer, Mississippi state leads Texas A&M early in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Mississippi State jumps out to early lead with 3-pointer

videos.description: Jasmine Lumpkin drives past the defender and makes the and-1 layup to give Texas A&M the lead over Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Texas A&M converts on and-1 layup to take the lead

videos.description: Texas A&M's Danni Williams hits the 3-pointer and then Mississippi State's Morgan William makes the jumper as time expires in the first quarter to cut into the Aggies' lead.
videos.headline: Texas A&M and Mississippi State trade buckets at end of first quarter

videos.description: Mississippi State regains the lead over Texas A&M after Victoria Vivians makes the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Vivians capitalizes on second chance to make 3-pointer

videos.description: Mississippi State's Chinwe Okorie gathers the entry pass and makes the easy layup to extend the lead over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Okorie gets position down low for easy layup

videos.description: Mississippi State's Breanna Richardson makes the 3-pointer at the end of the second quarter to extend the lead to double digits.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Richardson nails 3-pointer to beat halftime buzzer

videos.description: Mississippi State head coach, Vic Schaefer, breaks down the improvements his team needs to make in the second half against Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Schaefer: team needs to guard better in the second half

videos.description: Morgan William connects with Victoria Vivians  on the long outlet pass for the transition layup to increase Mississippi State's lead over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Vivians gets free in transition for bucket

videos.description: Victoria Vivians  makes the and-1 layup in transition to extend Mississippi State's lead over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Mississippi State continues strong play with and-1

videos.description: Texas A&M's Khaalia Hillsman rejects the shot attempt to prevent Roshunda Johnson from scoring but Mississippi State remains in the lead.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Hillsman swats shot attempt

videos.description: Texas A&M cuts into the Mississippi State lead after forcing a turnover and scoring on a fast break layup.
videos.headline: Texas A&M remains within striking distance with fast break layup

videos.description: Mississippi State head coach Vic Schaefer talks about his team's winning combination against Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Bulldogs rebound from first loss, get win over Aggies
